The paper deals with multi-document summarization, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.DL (Deep Learning).
